>Description:
In 5.3.1.10 on Vista, the tool-tips for the HtDP languages in the Choose Language Dialog appear and then immediately disappear, repeating indefinitely - sometimes too fast for the OS to register, sometimes not - causing an intermittent flash. (Doesn't seem to happen with DP languages, but does for the Legacy and Experimental languages).
